      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy confirmed for momentum and pressure equations (observed order 1.92 vs. theoretical 2.0). Hemolysis scalar transport verified only qualitatively; no manufactured-solution test for damage accumulation integral. Gap persists at MRL 5."
