      "rationale": "Validation data derive from the FDA generic centrifugal pump benchmark, which uses a simplified geometry. COU device is a commercial VAD with substantially different impeller geometry. Operating conditions partially overlap (3 of 5 points). Relevance gap is the largest single contributor to the Not-accepted recommendation."
